ory:English television producers]]\n[[Category:English-language film directors]]\n[[Category:Golden Globe Award-winning producers]]\n[[Category:Horror film directors]]\n[[Category:Hugo Award winners]]\n[[Category:Knights Bachelor]]\n[[Category:People from South Shields]]\n[[Category:Primetime Emmy Award winners]]\n[[Category:Royal Photographic Society]]\n[[Category:Science fiction film directors]]\n[[Category:Science Fiction Hall of Fame inductees]]\n[[Category:Television commercial directors]]\n[[Category:Scott family (filmmaking)]]\n", "name_user": "Arjayay", "label": "safe", "comment": "Duplicate word removed", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ridley_Scott"}
